- content_for(:title, 'フィードバック作成ページ')
%h1.text-center ご感想をお聞かせください！
.row
  .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
    = form_with(model: @feedback, local: true) do |f|
      = f.label :email
      = f.email_field :email, class: 'form-control'  
      = f.label :content
      = f.text_area :content, class: 'form-control'
      = f.submit "送信する", data: { disable_with: "送信中..." } ,class:"btn btn-primary"